			'rct_title': "3,000+ expert-designed workouts and counting",
			'rct_description': "From strength to mobility to heart-pumping Aero, Tonal workouts span over 15 categories and offer thousands of live and on-demand classes to keep you coming back, week after week.
			<br><br>Plus, explore programs designed to help you hit specific goals like Build Muscle, Get Lean, or Improve Fitness.",
